The repository provides the form of the metric functions and of auxiliary 
fields (as scalars) for black hole solutions in modified theories of gravity. 
The geodesic structure for massive/massless particles is also provided.

Depending on the theory, quantities are given in different functional forms, 
e.g., as small-spin expansions of the BH spin and of the theory coupling 
parameter (more details in main.nb).

Theories covered:
	•	Einstein–dilaton–Gauss–Bonnet gravity
	•	Dynamical Chern–Simons gravity
	•	Effective field theory extension of general relativity

